[337.061428, "o", "  ✓ snap: len=20,16 Tm=58.3,60.3 diff=2.0\r\n\r\n✓ All primer pairs meet requirements: True\r\n\r\n✓ BsaI-HF v2 recognition sites present: GGTCTC (fwd) and GAGACC (rev)\r\n"]
[337.061681, "o", "✓ Primers designed for one-pot Golden Gate assembly\r\n✓ Output file: primers.fasta\r\n\r\n=== ALL REQUIREMENTS MET ===\r\n"]
